# Dependabot — the community repo is a force-push mirror, so any PR
# merged on community gets overwritten by the next sync from private.
# That makes dependabot PRs on community functionally unmergeable and
# misleading to users browsing the public repo. Source of truth for
# dependency updates is the private repo; updates flow to community
# via the regular sync.
.github/dependabot.yml

